\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/sub\"><code>&lt;sub&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/summary\"><code>&lt;summary&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/sup\"><code>&lt;sup&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>T\n <ol>\n  <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/table\"><code>&lt;table&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tbody\"><code>&lt;tbody&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/td\"><code>&lt;td&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li class=\"webcomp\"><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/template\"><code>&lt;template&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/textarea\"><code>&lt;textarea&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tfoot\"><code>&lt;tfoot&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/th\"><code>&lt;th&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/thead\"><code>&lt;thead&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/time\"><code>&lt;time&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/title\"><code>&lt;title&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tr\"><code>&lt;tr&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/track\"><code>&lt;track&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><s class=\"obsoleteElement\"><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tt\"><code>&lt;tt&gt;</code></a></s></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>U\n <ol>\n  <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/u\"><code>&lt;u&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/ul\"><code>&lt;ul&gt;</code></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>V\n <ol>\n  <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/var\"><code>&lt;var&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/video\"><code>&lt;video&gt;</code></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>W\n <ol>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/wbr\"><code>&lt;wbr&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>X Y Z\n <ol>\n  <li><s class=\"obsoleteElement\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/xmp\"><code>&lt;xmp&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></s></li>\n </ol>\n    </li>\n   </ol>\n   </details></li>\n   </ol>\n  ","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p>Das <strong>HTML-Element <code>&lt;article&gt;</code></strong> stellt eine in sich geschlossene Komposition in einem Dokument, einer Seite, Anwendung oder Website dar, die unabhängig verteilt oder wiederverwendbar sein soll (z. B. bei Syndikation), z. B. ein Forumsbeitrag, ein Zeitschriften- oder Zeitungsartikel oder ein Blogeintrag.</p>\n\n<div id=\"sect2\"><iframe class=\"interactive\" height=\"445\" src=\"https://interactive-examples.mdn.mozilla.net/pages/tabbed/article.html\" title=\"MDN Web Docs Interactive Example\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe></div>\n\n<p class=\"hidden\">The source for this interactive example is stored in a GitHub repository. If you'd like to contribute to the interactive examples project, please clone <a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/interactive-examples\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">https://github.com/mdn/interactive-examples </a> and send us a pull request.</p>\n\n<p>Ein bestimmtes Dokument kann mehrere Artikel enthalten, z. B. in einem Blog, in dem der Text jedes Artikels nacheinander angezeigt wird, während der Leser blättert, wäre jeder Beitrag in einem <code>&lt;article&gt;</code>-Element mit einem oder mehreren <code>&lt;section&gt;</code>-Elementen enthalten.</p>\n\n<table class=\"properties\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Inhaltskategorien (en-US)</a></th>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#flow_content\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Fließender Inhalt (en-US)</a>, Sektionsinhalt, fühlbarer Inhalt</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Erlaubter Inhalt</th>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#flow_content\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Fließender Inhalt (en-US)</a>.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Tag Wegfall</th>\n   <td>Keine, sowohl das Anfangs- als auch das End-Tag sind erforderlich.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Erlaubte Elternelemente</th>\n   <td>Jedes Element das <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#flow_content\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">fließenden Inhalt (en-US)</a> erlaubt. Beachten Sie, dass ein <code>&lt;article&gt;</code>-Element kein Nachkomme eines <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/address\"><code>&lt;address&gt;</code></a>-Elements sein darf.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Erlaubte ARIA Rollen</th>\n   <td><code><a href=\"https://w3c.github.io/aria/#application\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">application</a></code>, <code><a href=\"https://w3c.github.io/aria/#document\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">document</a></code>, <code><a href=\"https://w3c.github.io/aria/#feed\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">feed</a></code>, <code><a href=\"https://w3c.github.io/aria/#main\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">main</a></code>, <code><a href=\"https://w3c.github.io/aria/#presentation\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">presentation</a></code>, <code><a href=\"https://w3c.github.io/aria/#region\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">region</a></code></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">DOM-Schnittstelle</th>\n   <td><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement\"><code>HTMLElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"attribute","title":"Attribute","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Dieses Element unterstützt nur die <a class=\"new\" href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Global_attributes\" rel=\"nofollow\">globalen Attribute</a>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"nutzungshinweise","title":"Nutzungshinweise","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li>Jeder <code>&lt;article&gt;</code> sollte beschriftet sein, normalerweise indem eine Überschrift (<a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Heading_Elements\"><code>&lt;h1&gt;</code>-<code>&lt;h6&gt;</code></a>) als untergeordnetes Element des <code>&lt;article&gt;</code>-Elements eingefügt wird.</li>\n <li>Wenn ein <code>&lt;article&gt;</code>-Element verschachtelt ist, repräsentiert das innere Element einen Artikel, der sich auf das äußere Element bezieht. Zum Beispiel können die Kommentare eines Blogbeitrags <code>&lt;article&gt;</code>-Elemente sein, die im <code>&lt;article&gt;</code> des Blogbeitrags verschachtelt sind.</li>\n <li>Informationen zum Autor eines <code>&lt;article&gt;</code>-Elements können über das <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/address\"><code>&lt;address&gt;</code></a>-Element bereitgestellt werden, gelten jedoch nicht für verschachtelte <code>&lt;article&gt;</code>-Elemente.</li>\n <li>Das Datum und die Uhrzeit der Veröffentlichung eines <code>&lt;article&gt;</code>-Elements können mit dem Attribut <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/time#attr-datetime\"><code>datetime</code></a> eines <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/time\"><code>&lt;time&gt;</code></a>-Elements beschrieben werden. <em>Beachten Sie, dass das Attribut <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/time#attr-pubdate\"><code>pubdate</code></a> von <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/time\"><code>&lt;time&gt;</code></a> nicht mehr Bestandteil des W3C HTML 5-Standards ist.</em></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"beispiele","title":"Beispiele","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>article</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>film_review<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>header</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>h2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Jurassic Park<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>h2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>header</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>section</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>main_review<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Dinos were great!<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>section</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>section</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>user_reviews<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>article</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>user_review<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n      <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Way too scary for me.<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n      <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>footer</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n        <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n          Posted on\n          <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>time</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">datetime</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>2015-05-16 19:00<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>May 16<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>time</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n          by Lisa.\n        <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n      <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>footer</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>article</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>article</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>user_review<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n      <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>I agree, dinos are my favorite.<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n      <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>footer</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n        <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n          Posted on\n          <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>time</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">datetime</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>2015-05-17 19:00<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>May 17<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>time</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n          by Tom.\n        <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n      <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>footer</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>article</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>section</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>footer</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n      Posted on\n      <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>time</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">datetime</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>2015-05-15 19:00<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>May 15<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>time</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n      by Staff.\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>footer</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>article</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"spezifikationen","title":"Spezifikationen","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Specification</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comment</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/semantics.html#the-article-element\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML Living Standard<br><small lang=\"de\">Die Definition von '&lt;article&gt;' in dieser Spezifikation.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Lebender Standard</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/html51/sections.html#the-article-element\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML 5.1<br><small lang=\"de\">Die Definition von '&lt;article&gt;' in dieser Spezifikation.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">Empfehlung</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/html52/sections.html#the-article-element\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML5<br><small lang=\"de\">Die Definition von '&lt;article&gt;' in dieser Spezifikation.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">Empfehlung</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Browserkompatibilität","id":"browserkompatibilität","isH3":false,"query":"html.elements.article","dataURL":"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/article/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"siehe_auch","title":"Siehe auch","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li>Andere abschnittsbezogene Elemente: <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/body\"><code>&lt;body&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/nav\"><code>&lt;nav&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/section\"><code>&lt;section&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/aside\"><code>&lt;aside&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Heading_Elements\"><code>&lt;h1&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Heading_Elements\"><code>&lt;h2&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Heading_Elements\"><code>&lt;h3&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Heading_Elements\"><code>&lt;h4&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Heading_Elements\"><code>&lt;h5&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Heading_Elements\"><code>&lt;h6&gt;</code></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/hgroup\"><code>&lt;hgroup&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/header\"><code>&lt;header&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/footer\"><code>&lt;footer&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/address\"><code>&lt;address&gt;</code></a></li>\n <li class=\"last\"><a class=\"deki-ns current page-not-created\" href=\"/de/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Sections_and_Outlines_of_an_HTML5_document\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\">Abschnitte und Umrisse eines HTML5-Dokuments</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Attribute","id":"attribute"},{"text":"Nutzungshinweise","id":"nutzungshinweise"},{"text":"Beispiele","id":"beispiele"},{"text":"Spezifikationen","id":"spezifikationen"},{"text":"Browserkompatibilität","id":"browserkompatibilität"},{"text":"Siehe auch","id":"siehe_auch"}],"summary":"Das HTML-Element <article> stellt eine in sich geschlossene Komposition in einem Dokument, einer Seite, Anwendung oder Website dar, die unabhängig verteilt oder wiederverwendbar sein soll (z. B. bei Syndikation), z. B. ein Forumsbeitrag, ein Zeitschriften- oder Zeitungsartikel oder ein Blogeintrag.","popularity":0.0004,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"<article>: The Article Contents element","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"article","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"<article> : l'élément de contenu d'un article","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"<article>: 記事コンテンツ要素","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"<article>","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"article (artigo)","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"<article>","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"<article>","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"de/web/html/element/article","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/de/web/html/element/article/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/de/docs/Web","title":"Webtechnologien für Entwickler"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/HTML","title":"HTML: HyperText Markup Language"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element","title":"Element"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/article","title":"<article>: Das Inhaltselement für Artikel"}],"pageTitle":"<article>: Das Inhaltselement für Artikel - HTML: HyperText Markup Language | MDN","noIndexing":false}}